# 1. Executive Summary

Phase 3 makes the platform **commercially usable, operationally safe, and extensible** for a one-time purchase model:

- Base plan purchase (one-time): `starter`, `pro`, or `ultra`
- Optional add-on bundles bought later (extra attempts, mock tests, materials)
- Plan controls **capability tier**; add-ons control **quantity only**
- Speaking module delivers full prompt rotation + bonus retry mechanics

---

# 2. Commercial Model

## 2.1 Plans

- `starter` — Free
- `pro` — $49.99 CAD one-time
- `ultra` — $99.99 CAD one-time

## 2.2 Add-on Types

**Consumable bundles:** 5 or 10 extra speaking attempts, 5 extra writing attempts, 2 extra mock tests  
**Unlock bundles:** learning materials pack, advanced practice pack, drill exercises pack  
**Hybrid bundles:** booster packs combining attempts + material unlocks

## 2.3 Core Rule — Add-ons Do Not Upgrade Capability

- Starter + extra attempts = more Starter-level attempts (not Pro reports)
- Pro + extra attempts = more Pro-level pipeline and reports
- Ultra + any add-on = Ultra-level throughout

