# 5. Product Decisions

## 5.1 Capability vs. Quantity

**Capability tier** (from base plan): AI depth, feedback richness, reporting, analytics, content richness  
**Quantity balance** (plan allowance + add-ons − used): how many times the user can act

## 5.2 Base Plan Behaviour

| | Starter | Pro | Ultra |
|---|---|---|---|
| Task practice | Locked | 5/task | 15/task |
| Speaking mocks | 1 | 2 | 5 |
| Writing mocks | 1 | 2 | 5 |
| AI feedback | Band estimate only | Full reports | Full + advanced |
| Analytics | None | History | Weak areas, trends |

## 5.3 Usage Policy

- Quota checked at attempt creation; add-ons consumed only on success
- Bonus retries: free, unlimited, same prompt, is_bonus_retry=true in DB
- No refund policy — all purchases are final

